reviewText: A UNIQUE EXPERIENCE.  HOWEVER, LOTS OF DUPLICATIONS OF EPISODES, FROM THE OTHER TAPES, BUT I JUST WATCH THEM "AGAIN".  I REALLY LIKE JUDGE ROY BEAN!
MY EXPERIENCE IN VIEWING THE TAPE, IS THAT IT IS AN EXCELLENT DVD.  HOWEVER, THERE WERE DUPLICATIONS IN VIEWING ALL OF THE TAPES.  I STILL LIKE JUDGE ROY BEAN!
